      "de": "My name is 朴若瑟."
    },
    {
      "zh": "我的家人叫我 Jen。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ de jiārén jiào wǒ Jen.",
      "de": "My family calls me Jen."
    },
    {
      "zh": "我有一個哥哥，我的哥哥喜歡打網球。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ yǒu yīgè gēge, wǒ de gēge xǐhuān dǎ wǎngqiú.",
      "de": "I have an older brother; my brother likes to play tennis."
    },
    {
      "zh": "我喜歡臺灣人，因為他們很好。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ xǐhuān Táiwān rén, yīnwèi tāmen hěn hǎo.",
      "de": "I like Taiwanese people because they are very nice."
    },
    {
      "zh": "我愛吃雞肉飯。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ ài chī jīròu fàn.",
